o the Griffiths picture of the slow transport in random systems.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 18 Jan 2021 11:54:44 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 4 May 2021 13:37:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-10-05"}
